<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:6.0pt;text-align:justify;mso-pagination:
none;background:white;mso-layout-grid-align:none;text-autospace:none'><span
style='letter-spacing:-.15pt'>ОТГОВОРИЛА РОЩА ЗОЛОТАЯ...</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='text-align:justify;mso-pagination:none;background:
